Issue tracker
-------------

Submit issues by sending a patch

Format
------

n: name
d: description
t: tags
i: optional email message-id for the issue

You can use In-Reply-To: <message-id> from your email client to comment on
this issue.

Example
-------

todo/issue-name.txt:

n: Some issue title
d: some 
t: feature,bug,cli
i: message-id
